description: Hottie Beaux Banks makes his Next Door debut, and making the welcome even warmer is long time Next Door exclusive, Dante Martin, who has a wee bit of a porn crush on Beaux, and much more than a wee bit of a hard on to prove it! Beaux is a walking fantasy, so he's probably used to the attention, but rest assured Dante has had this date circled on his calendar for quite some time, and now that he has him in his clutches, Beaux is in for one wild ride.Enjoy!
title: Beaux Banks' Warm Welcome
